p: Most of the compounds were aliphatic hydrocarbons and medium-long chain esters (C10-C20). There were also two alcohols (isoamyl alcohol and 2-ethyl-2-methyl-1-tridecanol), 1 phenol (2,4 di- tert-buthyl-phenol), 1 aldehyde ( n-hexadecanal) and 1 ketone (benzophenone).
